Package: indoorLocation
Title: Predicts Indoor Location of a Subject based on WIFI Fingerprint
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Paramjot", "Singh", email = "param.chhina@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package uses indoor location dataset (https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/UJIIndoorLoc#) for exploring different models to predict the indoor location of a subject relying on a WLAN/WIFI fingerprinting technology.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1

### Main Goals

- Get the data
- Carry out EDA to explore the data
- Fit candidate models
- Select top 2 or 3 models to evalutate performance on test set
- Select the best model
- Design the app
- Implement the best model in app
- Test and launch
